Modified files
--------------

This extension redistributes prebuilt binaries built from — and lightly
modified copies of — portions of the Tencent Hunyuan 3D 2.1 Works. The
modifications, relative to the pristine upstream sources, are:

- custom_rasterizer/setup.py — repointed from the Linux kernel sources
  (lib/custom_rasterizer_kernel/) to the MSVC-safe Windows kernel sources
  (lib/custom_rasterizer_kernel_for_windows/).
- custom_rasterizer_kernel_for_windows/rasterizer_gpu.cu — z_min dtype fix
  (.data_ptr<uint64_t>() -> .data_ptr<int64_t>()) so the Long tensor loads at
  run time; the existing (uint64_t*) cast still reinterprets the bits.
- utils/multiview_utils.py and hunyuanpaintpbr/pipeline.py — phase-offload
  staging edits (moving stage weights between GPU and CPU to fit lower-VRAM
  cards) applied by the extension at install time.

The prebuilt artifacts under prebuilt/win_amd64-cp311-cu128/ are compiled from
these sources; see prebuilt/win_amd64-cp311-cu128/PROVENANCE.md for exact build
inputs and checksums.

